

1. 'useradd fibbles'

2. 'passwd fibbles'

3. 'su fibbles'

4. 'ssh-keygen'

5. Disable by prepending "!" to the password in '/etc/shadow':

    /etc/passwd:
    fibbles:x:1004:1004::/home/fibbles:/bin/bash
    
    /etc/shadow:
    fibbles:!$6$kbonnOKB$iLPZ2GfAOiOx0EUo3/FzN6bpMYeokYwPruwwJ2u/cljDHh8vMglNG19aGS3ZATnCcp9fU/DbibIZ1nJtDZUak/:16408:0:99999:7:::
    
    /home/fibbles/.ssh/id_rsa.pub:
    ssh-rsa  fibbles@comp270-46

6. Mail does not bounce
